target.echo:
Supported targets (default=compile): ------------------------------------------------------------------------- check - checks if all needed binary and source libraries are available. compile - compile all project files. javadoc - build project javadoc files dist - will create a complete binary and source distribution clean - will clean up files, except the source files and the api documentation cvsupdate - gets the latest ${project.name.full} version from the developer CVS repository. tutorial - builds the DocBook tutorial and all descriptors and algorithm informations (requires DocBook, Jade, Convert ...)
use 'ant -projecthelp' for further Main targets ------------------------------------------------------------------------- Mailing lists: http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/${project.name.cvs}-devel http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/${project.name.cvs}-help
${project.name.full}@SourceForge: http://sourceforge.net/projects/${project.name.cvs}
